channel.title: Excl is gone
channel.description: So I was bored today sort of so I went on to youtube to watch some of my old favorites. I had no idea that Excl had quit recently. Apparently about a week/two week ago he just ...literally vanished off the map. Nobody has seen him, both of his channels are gone, his facebook is gone, etc.
